{"tid":642902,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有精神病，抑鬱，焦慮，精神分裂的討論","createTime":"2018-04-26T06:30:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-04T06:00:54.000Z","uid":40997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d1c333116e67d997ef4dbc6f5197055f879b7dab","tid":642902,"uid":40997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T06:30:07.000Z","msg":"除左日常的症狀，你地有冇試過d好奇怪的症狀，後來解唔解決到？<br />\n<br />\n我自己就上年情緒唔好 左後腦有個位痛到依家 之後嗅覺減弱左 味覺冇事 ，長年肌肉跳動<br />\n<br />\n我應該睇咩科去處理幾上問題？我同精神科醫生講過 佢地覺得一切都係焦慮諗成 但事實唔係<br />\n<br />\n求巴絲解答"},{"pid":"e8adc1263982551f4cfb023f5bcab083ffa1bdd0","tid":642902,"uid":178110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T06:34:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e8ce69833a8d5274008b6935f198e3442949a9a1","tid":642902,"uid":37240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T06:35:39.000Z","msg":"大壓力？<br />\n壓力大都會咁"},{"pid":"35f2871d17ad4b7ee02b8a2bbb83e654c4900685","tid":642902,"uid":74262,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T06:36:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2544e8ab7d944b0aa9b2259b8a42f9975582cda9","tid":642902,"uid":40997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35f2871d17ad4b7ee02b8a2bbb83e654c4900685","tid":642902,"uid":74262,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T06:36:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T07:23:03.000Z","msg":"照過冇事"},{"pid":"1de1223f0ba34f3ed83486ca24b52024632f460a","tid":642902,"uid":19978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T07:32:06.000Z","msg":"長年肌肉跳動同反胃作嘔"},{"pid":"362bb9cd0eb565ade4b9dd77a5e867445a9175c6","tid":642902,"uid":40997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1de1223f0ba34f3ed83486ca24b52024632f460a","tid":642902,"uid":19978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T07:32:06.000Z","msg":"長年肌肉跳動同反胃作嘔"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T07:50:43.000Z","msg":"咩症"},{"pid":"de03fbcb54728fc5f195ff9edd5c3ac